_sText:
Here is a new bombsite - hostage rescue map!

I believe the map works great.
A maximum of 32 players are able to play the map at once. It has several props, a good lightning, good shadows, and some effects (fire,smoke).

For any mistakes please do not flag the map, rather comment and I will upload new files as soon as possible.

Didn't really know on what section to put this map since there is a bombsite and a hostage rescue goal, so I went with Fight Yard, since its more about killing all your opponents first. 

I like this map, so I intend to make a night version of it. (gonna make it soon) To install this map simply put the new cstrike folder over the old one and overwrite.

Comments, suggestions and ratings are welcome! :P

(the map is also very good for playing with boots)
